lyrics:
#DareToZlatan LyricsHi @Twitter. For tomorrow Zlatan needs more than 140 characters. Please change rules for Zlatan #DareToZlatan

Need help to ZLATAN? Learn to take the risks that make legends. Ask questions. Learn the ways. #DareToZlatan

Dear @EdgleyLFC. Daring to Zlatan is easy. Start by trying moves that can’t be done. Keep trying until you are Zlatan. #DareToZlatan
Incorporate Zlatan’s teachings into your life, @life_of_eisen, and one day @NikeFootball might make a t-shirt named after you. #DareToZlatan

Zlatan applauds the number of times you got Zlatan into one sentence, @jflint91. Always do what others don't have guts to try. #DareToZlatan

There are 2 things Zlatan cannot do @at_sunshine. One is be predictable. The other is a step-under. But Zlatan is practising. #DareToZlatan
Am I mad @bailofwz? Would a sane man try a 32 yard overhead kick in an international match? #DareToZlatan
To Zlatan like Zlatan, practice with pressure. As the heat rises, so will your game. #DareToZlatan http://youtu.be/29Po75THraU

Hey, @Areeb23. Learn to unlearn the word ‘safe’. Because if you don’t know what it means you can’t play it. #DareToZlatan

Dear @ArmouredGuy, a wise man once said, surprising your opponent is the key to surprising them. That wise man was Zlatan. #DareToZlatan

@EurosportCom_FR Let’s work together. Zlatan scores the goals, Eurosport writes them up. Deal? #DareToZlatan
Hi @Greg_douglass, failure is the first step to success. The second step is growing a ponytail. #DaretoZlatan

@MillarHarry Because two Zlatans would just be unfair. #DareToZlatan

@AAlasfoor10 Zlatan’s favourite stadium is the one with grass and two goals. Every stadium is a potential stage. #DareToZlatan

Set-piece perfection shows true inner peace. Use this to train your pressure muscles. #DareToZlatan

When the heat becomes unbearable, there’s only one thing to do. Make it hotter.#DareToZlatan

When it comes to dealing with pressure follow this tip. #DareToZlatan

To Zlatan is to embrace your fears and take the risks necessary to overcome them. #DareToZlatan http://youtu.be/7SBnk3lKzzg

Dear @AmirunSalleh, nothing Zlatan does is easy. That's why Zlatan does it. #DareToZlatan
Hi @rumadbro00 self-belief leads to self-confidence. Self-confidence leads to self-belief which leads to self-confidence again #DareToZlatan

@AlotibeH Zlatan admires your daring. The only goalkeeper in the world who hopes to play against Zlatan. #DareToZlatan

Dear @Khaledsaifi. Zlatan used this simple thought process. #DareToZlatan

@KHow20 @CRiegg18 Weaker feet are there to be weak so you always have something to improve. Take the shot. #DareToZlatan

Fear to Zlatan is like gas to a turbo charged sports car. The more you put in the further you go. #DareToZlatan

Hey @citralistyarini. You'll never score a diving header if you keep your feet on the ground. #DareToZlatan

Need to impress a scout? Take risks to score great goals. If that doesn't work, try this. #DareToZlatan

@101greatgoals #DareToZlatan: dare to miss in order to score. Risk to lose in order to win. If in doubt use this.

Take risks and surprise your opponents. Once you've done that, send them one of these. #DareToZlatan

Yes @Tom_J_Webster. Zlatan is just a human. The same way a great white shark is just a fish. #DareToZlatan

@delce_1004 Zlatan’s best goal is always his next. #DaretoZlatan

@Eymen144 Some players train to be one step ahead of the game. Zlatan trains to be two steps ahead of the world. #DareToZlatan

@JesperBulykin Fear for breakfast, defenders for lunch, and pickled herring for dinner. #DareToZlatan
@itsLeRoy_ You have passed stage one of #DareToZlatan. Next step, a 34 yard shot. With your other foot.

To Zlatan you must trust your instincts, think one step ahead. Only then will risk become reflex. #DareToZlatan http://youtu.be/Nxm6Y_v7_SA

@NathanBKShanko It does when Zlatan uses it as a blindfold. #DareToZlatan http://giphy.com/gifs/44BwAV2lhCqRGFcnKKY?tc=1

@JordanWilsonn7 The only thing Zlatan can’t do is play it safe in the face of danger. #DareToZlatan http://giphy.com/gifs/pg9suKHtCDql3RUi5i?tc=1

@ibbyAbd8 It was skill that Zlatan scored it. Luck that Zlatan is Swedish. #DareToZlatan

@HazardIsLife With belief. You may have to wait til the last minute for your first chance. But when it comes #DaretoZlatan, like Zlatan.

@niallmcg86 Zlatan does score tap ins. From 33 yards. With his heel. #DareToZlatan

@christiaaannzz Pressure makes adrenalin. Adrenalin makes performance. Performance makes Zlatan. Zlatan makes grown men cry. #DaretoZlatan

@MattCrivelli ‘Worst’ isn’t in Zlatan’s vocabulary. Although ‘goal’ is frequently used. #DareToZlatan

@AyyeitsArv Trust your instincts. Learn to see a bicycle kick as nothing more than an upside-down volley. #DareToZlatan

@koerazak You don’t need Zlatan to teach you. When you believe in yourself, Zlatan is there. #DareToZlatan

Today’s been good. Continue as Zlatan has taught you. If ever in doubt. Use this. #DareToZlatan5Embed
